Hello John,

Thank you for taking the time to meet today.

Today we:

Identified two views that provide the desired data for the Passwords report. This includes the OpenShares_SDDDetails and the FS_SharesRanked_SDD views. We then modified the current report to display 2 rows including both of these views. This will display two sets of information from both views in one report.

Our next steps are:

You will:

Generate the report with the updated modifications and provide the results of the report.

I will:

Keep this ticket open to allow for report generation and review of the data that's populated in the report.

Thank you,

Scottie Taylor
